\c 18
\s Abhurahamu anonyengeterera Sodhomu
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakazviratidza kwaari pamiti yemiouki yeMa­mure, agere pamusuo wetende masikati zuva richipisa;
\v 2 akasimudza meso ake, akatarira, akaona varume vatatu vamire vakatarisana naye; akati achivaona, aka­bva pamusuo wetende, akamhanya ku­ndosangana navo, akakotamira pasi,
\v 3 akati, Ishe wangu, kana ndawana nya­sha kwamuri, musapfuura henyu pamura­nda wenyu.
\v 4 Ngavauye nemvura shoma­nana, mushambidze tsoka dzenyu, muzorore pasi pomuti;
\v 5 ini nditore chi­medu chechingwa, musimbise moyo yenyu; mugozopfuura henyu, nekuti ndi­zvo zvamauyira kumuranda wenyu. Ivo vakati; ita hako sezvawataura
\p
\v 6 Abhurahamu akakurumidza kupi­nda mutende kuna Sara, akati, Kurumi­dza ugadzire zviyero zvitatu zvoupfu hwakatsetseka, ukanye, ubike zvingwa zviduku.
\p
\v 7 Naiye Abhurahamu akamhanyira kumombe, akatora mhuru ine nyama yakapfava, yakanaka, akapa muranda wake, iye akakurumidza kuigadzira.
\v 8 Akatora mukaka wakafa, nomukaka, nemhuru yaakanga agadzira, akazviisa pamberi pavo; akamira navo munyasi momuti, vakadya.
\p
\v 9 Ivo vakati kwaari, Sara, mukadzi wako, ari kupiko? Iye akati, Tarirai, ari mutende.
\v 10 Iye akati, Zvirokwazvo, kana gore rapfuura, ndichauyazve kwa­muri, nenguva iyo Sara, mukadzi wako, achava nomwanakomana. Zvino Sara akanga achiteerera ari pamusuo wetende shure kwake.
\v 11 Zvino Abhurahamu naSara vakanga vakwegura, vava namakore mazhinji; nomutoo wavakadzi wakanga watoguma kuna Sara.
\v 12 Sara akaseka mumoyo make akati, Ini ndingazvifa­rira here zvandachembera, naiye tenzi wangu akwegurawo?
\v 13 Jehovha akati kuna Abhurahamu, Sara wasekereiko, achiti, Ko ini muchembere ndichabereka mwana zvirokwazvo here?
\v 14 Kune chi­nhu chingakunda Jehovha here? Nguva ino, gore rapfuura, ndichadzokera kwauri; Sara achava nomwanakomana.
\p
\v 15 Asi Sara akaramba achiti, Ha­ndina kuseka, nekuti akanga achitya. Iye akati, Kwete waseka hako.
\p
\v 16 Zvino vaya varume vakasimuka, vakabva ipapo, vakatarira Sodhomu; Abhurahamu akaenda navo achivapere­kedza.
\v 17 Zvino Jehovha akati, Ndicha­vanzira Abhurahamu zvandinoita here?
\v 18 Abhurahamu zvaachava rudzi rukuru rune simba, nendudzi dzose dzenyika dzicharopafadzwa maari?
\v 19 nekuti nda­kamutsaura, kuti araire vana vake navei­mba yake vanomutevera, kuti vache­ngete nzira yaJehovha, vaite zvakarurama nezvakanaka; kuti Jehovha auyise pamusoro paAbhurahamu izvo zvaakataura pamusoro pake.
\p
\v 20 Ipapo Jehovha akati, Kudanidzira kweSodhomu neGomora kukuru kwazvo; zvirokwazvo zvivi zvavo zvakaipa kwa­zvo;
\v 21 ndichaburuka zvino kuti ndione izvo zvavaita, kana zvakafanana nokuda­nidzira kwavo kwakasvika kwandiri; kana zvisina kudaro, ndichazviziva.
\p
\v 22 Zvino vaya varume vakabva, va­kaenda Sodhomu; asi Abhurahamu aka­ramba amire pamberi paJehovha.
\v 23 Zvino Abhurahamu wakaswedera, akati, Mu­chaparadza vakarurama pamwechete na­vakaipa here?
\v 24 Zvimwe vangavapo va­karurama vana makumi mashanu muguta; muchaparadza nzvimbo iyo, mu­kasainzwira tsitsi nokuda kwavakaru­rama vana makumi mashanu varimo here?
\v 25 Ngazvive kure nemwi kuita kudaro kuuraya vakarurama pamwechete nava­kaipa, kuti vakarurama vave savakaipa, ngazvive kure nemi. Mutongi wenyika yose haangaiti zvakarurama here?
\p
\v 26 Ipapo Jehovha akati, Kana ndika­wana muSodhomu vakarurama vana ma­kumi mashanu mukati meguta, ndicha­nzwira nzvimbo yose tsitsi nokuda kwavo.
\p
\v 27 Abhurahamu akapindura akati, Tarirai zvino, ndatsunga kutaura naJeho­vha, ini guruva nedota hangu;
\v 28 zvimwe kuchashaikwa vashanu kuvakarurama vana makumi mashanu; mungaparadza guta rose kana vashanu vashaikwa here? Akati, Handingariparadzi, kana ndikawa­namo makumi mana navashanu.
\p
\v 29 Akataurazve naye akati, Zvimwe kuchawanikwamo makumi mana. Akati, Handingazviiti nokuda kwamakumi mana.
\p
\v 30 Akati, Jehovha ngaarege hake kunditsamwira, kana ndikataurazve. Zvi­mwe vana makumi matatu vachawani­kwamo. Akati, Handingazviiti, kana ndikawana makumi matatu.
\p
\v 31 Akati, Tarirai, ndatsunga kutaura naJehovha, zvimwe vana makumi maviri vachawanikwamo. Akati, Handingari­paradzi nokuda kwamakumi maviri.
\p
\v 32 Akati, Jehovha ndikataurazve ka­mwe chete; zvimwe vane gumi rimwe chete vangawanikwamo.
\p Akati, Handingariparadzi nokuda kwaivavo vane gumi.
\v 33 Ipapo Jehovha akabva, apedza kutaura naAbhurahamu; naAbhurahamu akadzokera kumba kwake.
